And the [INAUDIBLE]
is on the next slide,

00:35:13.060 --> 00:35:18.430
which is the combined result
of the 2011 and the 2012.

00:35:18.430 --> 00:35:26.070
OK, so this is the
p-value of 2011 and 2012.

00:35:26.070 --> 00:35:30.290
This black one, this
is the combined.

00:35:30.290 --> 00:35:33.422
You can see it's beyond
[INAUDIBLE], one, two, three,

00:35:33.422 --> 00:35:34.724
and four.

00:35:34.724 --> 00:35:36.632
[LAUGHTER]

