beauty in the human activities

00:48:28.270 --> 00:48:30.120
in the search for
the Higgs boson,

00:48:30.120 --> 00:48:34.370
and I would like to bring
that from that phase space

00:48:34.370 --> 00:48:37.640
to the larger phase
space of human beings,

00:48:37.640 --> 00:48:43.640
to bring the beauty into the
consciousness of human beings.

00:48:43.640 --> 00:48:45.350
But in the same
time, I would also

00:48:45.350 --> 00:48:48.950
like to explore and
observe and listen

00:48:48.950 --> 00:48:53.560
to the stories of other people
to see how can we work together

00:48:53.560 --> 00:48:56.690
towards a future,
and which direction

00:48:56.690 --> 00:49:00.420
that I can contribute the best
in the future to the humanity.

